		<title>13Leisure and Recreation</title>
		<content> There is a youth centre on Longlands  
 Road. It is used by schools, the two  
 football clubs (senior, junior teams) 
 and other organisations, also there   
 are badminton courts. There is a      
 cricket club on Church Road which has 
 senior and junior teams. There is also
 a cricket  ground in Low Leighton.    
 There are parks and play areas        
 scattered all over New Mills. Two of  
 the biggest are High Lea and Wirksmoor
 Recreational ground.                  
                                       
                                       
                                       
                                       
                                       
                                       
                                       
                                       
                                       
